# Paths excluded from Nox security scanning. Format: gitignore-style.
#
# Reason for each entry — keep current so reviewers know why something
# is suppressed. Run `nox scan` after editing to confirm the exclusion
# took effect.

# npm/pnpm lockfiles: sha512 integrity hashes false-match every imported
# gitleaks "Detected X API Key" pattern (Firebase, ELK Stack, IBM Cloud,
# Prometheus, Literal, etc.). These are public deterministic hashes,
# not credentials. Real dep CVEs are still tracked via VULN-001.
**/package-lock.json
**/yarn.lock
**/pnpm-lock.yaml

# Demo environment: intentionally weak fixed creds (temper:temper). Not
# production. Documented at top of the file.
docker-compose.demo.yml

# .env example file: documents env-var names with placeholder values.
.env.example
